Job Description

  Handle full operations of the restaurant/outlet sales, profit and people management
  Responsible for the hiring &amp; retention of full-time and flexi-hourly rated crew members
  Plan employee strength and roster
  Lead and train a team of dedicated service providers
  Manage inventory control and usage

Industry Background &amp; Skills

  Possess at least 1year relevant experience in the same capacity
  Good communication and interpersonal skills
  Positive mindset and a passion in providing excellent guest service.
  Good team-player, team leader and have the ability to prioritize in a fast-paced environment
